{
  "stem": "2373.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The thirst was worse than hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was June, June, July.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, my-- my friends and my family were always thirsty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know the feeling of thirst.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I was only hungry, not thirsty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After five or six weeks--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then one morning, we noticed that I have spots on my tummy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, well, we knew straight away that this infectious disease, scarlet fever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that was raging then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shall we say something, or shall we keep it quiet?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then we thought-- I was always together with my cousin and with my two aunties.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We said, well, I can infect everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to say it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went to the-- the barrack had a doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We showed her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she says yes, that's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, next morning, you are coming with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We are going to the truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So next morning, on the corner every morning, there was a truck collecting dead infectious diseases or the dead people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were marching to that truck with the doctor and with my cousin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the doctor said, give her your shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You don't need them anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So what--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what she said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Judzi-- is my cousins name-- she didn't want my shoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I stayed in my shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came to that corner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is no truck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where is the truck?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That morning, a barrack was opened up for infectious diseases.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody who had scarlet fever or typhus came into that room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spent the next six weeks on the floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So although it was for infectious diseases, it wasn't a hospital or anything like that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't a hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a special barrack for infectious disease.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
